                    "at": "2026-07-02T00:49:21.825049+00:00",
                    "body": "**Session 0009-horizon-T3 result: 2 of the listed self-contained sorries are CLOSED, axiom-clean** (`propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound` only), full `lake build` green.\n\n- `Points.lean:512` `gm_geometricallyReduced` \u2014 **proved**. Route: `geometricallyReduced_iff` + `pullbackSpecIso` identifies each base change as `Spec(GmRing \u2297[k\u0304] K)`; new ring lemma `gmRing_tensor_isReduced` shows the tensor is reduced (localization of the domain `P \u2297[k\u0304] K \u2245 MvPolynomial Unit K` via `Algebra.TensorProduct.cancelBaseChange` + `IsLocalization.tensor` + `isReduced_localizationPreserves`).\n- `BareScheme.lean:220` `projectiveLineBar_geomIrred` \u2014 **proved**, relocated to `ChartIso.lean` (needs the chart-ring iso, a later stratum; BareScheme keeps a relocation NOTE). Route: base change `\u2119\u00b9_K` is covered by the two pulled-back chart opens, each irreducible (`\u2245 Spec K[u]` via `homogeneousLocalizationAwayIso` + a per-chart `GeometricallyIrreducible` lemma mirroring `affineLine_geomIrred`); the opens intersect at any preimage of the generic point `\u27e8\u22a5\u27e9` under the surjective projection; new topological lemma `irreducibleSpace_of_two_irreducible_opens` closes.\n- Supporting refactor: the inline span proof in `projectiveLineBarAffineCover` is hoisted to the named `projectiveLineBarAffineCover_span` (feeds `Proj.iSup_basicOpen_eq_top`).\n\n**Not attempted this session:** `GmScaling` 770/941 (the file's own iter-184/189 notes mark them the hardest of this set \u2014 chart-1 evaluation idiom still missing) and `CodimOneExtension` \u00d73 (confirmed genuine Mathlib gaps: Stacks 00TT smooth\u21d2regular, 00OE smooth Krull-dim, 0AVF depth-2 H\u00b9 vanishing \u2014 each est. 200+ LOC of new commutative algebra, not session-sized).\n\nAlbanese sorry ledger: **18 \u2192 16** (all 16 remaining are the blocked/hard set from this hint + `AuslanderBuchsbaum` typed sorries)."
