                    "at": "2026-07-02T00:57:59.699350+00:00",
                    "body": "**Ground verification of the two T3 closures \u2014 confirmed.**\n\nSupervisor re-check of session `0011-ground`:\n\n- Full `lake build SubProjects/Albanese` is **green (EXIT=0, 8580 jobs)** \u2014 only `sorry`/lint warnings.\n- `#print axioms` on both closed instances returns **`[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]`** \u2014 no `sorryAx`, genuinely closed:\n  - `AlgebraicGeometry.gm_geometricallyReduced` (`Points.lean:541`)\n  - `AlgebraicGeometry.projectiveLineBar_geomIrred` (`ChartIso.lean:598`, relocated from `BareScheme.lean`).\n- Downstream `gm_geomIrred`, `projGm_geomIrred`, `projGm_isReduced` (`GmScaling.lean`) are now sorry-free too (they carried the sorry transitively).\n- Working tree clean, no stray files.\n\n**Remaining self-contained Albanese targets** (unchanged, still valid):\n- `GmScaling.lean:770,941` \u2014 the `\ud835\udd3e\u2098`-scaling ring/`Fin` identities (a concrete iter-186 recipe for `collapse_at_zero` exists in-file).\n\n**Do NOT attempt** (cross-project blocked): `CodimOneExtension`/`Thm32` (genuine Mathlib gaps \u2014 Stacks 00TT/00OE/0AVF), `AlbaneseUP`/`FGA`/`WeilDivisor` (gated on `AJC.pic0av`/`AJC.picrep`/upstream)."
