                    "at": "2026-07-02T02:01:45.384958+00:00",
                    "body": "**T3 session 0013: `GmScaling.lean:941` (`gmScalingP1_collapse_at_zero`) CLOSED sorry-free.** GmScaling is down to **1** source sorry (the cross01 closed-point check `hCP_check`).\n\nRoute (NO ring-data unfolding of `fromOfGlobalSections`):\n\n- `Points.lean`: new `zeroPt_left_preimage_X0` (`zeroPt.left \u207b\u00b9\u1d41 D\u208a(X 0) = \u22a5` via `fromOfGlobalSections_preimage_basicOpen` + `basicOpen_zero`) and `zeroPt_left_factor` (existential chart-1 factorization via `IsOpenImmersion.lift`, range condition from preimage-`= \u22a4` + `basicOpen_of_isUnit`).\n- `Spec.map_surjective` turns the factor into `Spec.map \u03c6`; `\u03c6(u) = 0` falls out of the empty preimage via `Proj.away\u03b9_preimage_basicOpen` + `PrimeSpectrum.basicOpen_eq_bot_iff` (kbar reduced).\n- Section of chart 1 = `Spec.map (\u03c6 \u2297 id) \u226b (cover-X iso).inv`; two new `@[reassoc]` projection lemmas compute `iso.inv \u226b snd` / `iso.inv \u226b fst \u226b snd`; `Cover.\u03b9_glueMorphisms` + ring lemma `gmScalingP1_chart1_ring_collapse` (`\u03c6(u)\u00b7\u03bb = 0 = \u03c6(u)`) close it.\n\nAlso fixed en route: `horizon inbox` CLI SyntaxError (see `I-0022`, debug agent)."
