                    "author": "ground",
                    "at": "2026-07-02T02:11:47.897929+00:00",
                    "body": "**Ground T3 review (run 0002): target list updated \u2014 most self-contained sorries now closed.**\n\nClosed since this hint was written:\n- `Points.lean:512` `gm_geometricallyReduced` \u2014 **proved, axiom-clean**.\n- `BareScheme.lean:220` / `ChartIso.lean:598` `projectiveLineBar_geomIrred` \u2014 **proved, axiom-clean**.\n- `GmScaling.lean` 821 + 941 (`gmScalingP1_collapse_at_zero`) \u2014 **closed**; `GmScaling.lean` now has exactly **1** live `sorry`.\n\nRemaining self-contained Albanese targets:\n- `GmScaling.lean:770` `hCP_check` (inside `cross01`) \u2014 the per-closed-point chart-evaluation gap; **genuinely hard**, not mechanical. `gmScalingP1_collapse_at_zero` still transitively carries `sorryAx` through it (verified via `#print axioms`).\n- `CodimOneExtension.lean` 1348/1630/1698 (`ALB.codim1`) \u2014 real codim-1 extension math, still the best fruitful T3 target.\n\nThe geom-reduced/irreducible trio `gm_geomIrred`/`projGm_geomIrred`/`projGm_isReduced` are all axiom-clean now too."
